    "attributes": {
        "action": "Tax Relief for Blue Light Workers ",
        "additional_details": "Due to high tax rates on additional income, I think our earnings are significantly reduced, leaving us inadvertently financially penalised for working extra hours. I believe this discourages essential workers from taking on vital shifts, particularly at a time when our critical public services are under immense pressure. Tax relief could provide fair compensation for our hard work and dedication.",
        "background": "Introduce a tax relief for Blue Light workers taking on extra shifts or working second jobs to ensure fair compensation. I think that high tax rates reduce earnings and discourage extra work.",
